title: Arena City [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
In Arena City, the city was attacked by aliens and you need to destroy them all. From their robot ships, they land soldiers and robots. Destroy the robot ship and more enemies will stop landing. For fast movement, use teleporters. A large number of bonuses and additional weapons, as well as dynamic gameplay and good music await you. Kill all the enemies and save the city!

Control keys:

WASD - Character Movement
SPACEBAR - Jump
SHIFT - Sprint
1,2,3,4,5...- Weapon change
R - Reload
Esc - Exit the menu
LMB - Shoot
RMB - Aim


System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 мmb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 378 mb
